COPY public.love_letters (id, title, date, content, created_at) FROM stdin;
f924c37c-4570-44b7-9f6c-999fa76110d4	Proposal Shayari	2024-05-23	Jabse aapko dekha hai,\nTabse dekhte hei rehe gaye....\nJabse aapko jana hai,\nTabse jante hei rehe gaye...\nPehele laga tha ke aap jada bolti nhi ho,\nPar jabse aapko suna hai,\nTabse sunte hei rehe gaye...\nTabse sunte hei rehe gaye...\n\nbus wale din toh,\nEk soft corner sa ho gaya...\nJabse aapke sath safar kiya hai,\nEk emotion sa ho gaya....\nAb toh koi aur safar achhe lagte hei nhi mujhe...\nJabse aapke sath gaane sune hai,\nEk attachment sa ho gaya...\nEk attachment sa ho gaya...\n\nAb kuch baate seedhe batana chahata hu...\nAb kuch intezaar khatam karna chahata hu...\nLog toh ek dure ko...phool deke izhaar karte hai...\nPar mae ye, KitKat se karna chahata hu...\nKitKat se karna chahata hu...	2025-05-23 12:21:27.420794+00
dd831a81-0f8b-4168-8e17-b2e876deab68	Birthday Poem (Before Relationship)	2024-01-15	Mile thae hum handball ke maidan mai,\nAap aai thi shreyasi ke sath mai...\nAapne humse pucha tha handball ke bare mai,\nTabse baat-chit shuru hui thi humare aur app mai...\n\nHandball ka safar kafi yaadgaarr safar ban jayega,\nAisa socha nhi tha...\nEk random si ladki itni achhi dost ban jayegi,\nAisa laga nhi tha....\n\nRumours toh faile humare bare mai kafi saree,\nBut humare dosti pe affect hua nhi tha...\nLogo ko laga humara rishta thoda zada,\nPar humare beech kuch badla nhi tha....\n\nMulakate toh humari sari yaadgaar thi,\nChahe vo havan ka din ho,\nJab aapne kit-kat diya tha...\nChahe humari train ki mulakat.\nJab humne key chain diya tha...\nYa jab hum vashi gaye thae,\nYa jab aapne my bottle diya tha....\nYa jab allen ke badh aapse milne aaye thae...\nYa jab aapne hume hug kiya tha...\n\nYe safar toh kafi yaadgaar tha humara,\nIsse aur bhi yaadgaar banayenge...\nSath toh rahenge hum aapke humesha,\nAise chodhke toh nhi jayenge...\nAise chodhke toh nhi jayenge....\n\nHAPPY BIRTHDAY 🎂 🥳	2025-05-24 07:33:55.62018+00
\.


